  <brief_title>Study to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of CD-NP in the Treatment of Patients With Acute Decompensated Heart Failure</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-Center, Single-Blind, Placebo-Controlled Phase 2 Study Assessing the Safety and Efficacy of Intravenous CD-NP in the Treatment of Patients With Acute Decompensated Heart Failure</official_title>
