  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of the study is to assess the safety and tolerability of IV
      administration of CD-NP and the dose relationship of CD-NP on improvement of clinical
      symptoms and renal function in ADHF patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
